    {
      "start": 563.36,
      "end": 564.04,
      "text": "Oh, sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 564.22,
      "end": 564.72,
      "text": "Go ahead."
    },
    {
      "start": 564.8,
      "end": 566.62,
      "text": "Yeah, she chose another life."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.0,
      "end": 569.88,
      "text": "엄마는 다른 인생을 선택하셨어."
    },
    {
      "start": 570.32,
      "end": 573.92,
      "text": "And it's not like your dad and my mom didn't like us."
    },
    {
      "start": 574.1,
      "end": 578.76,
      "text": "네, and it's not like your dad and my mom didn't like us."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.92,
      "end": 580.2,
      "text": "네, 전체 들으셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.12,
      "end": 585.64,
      "text": "엄마가 새로운 삶을 선택하고 떠나셨다라는 말은 결국"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.64,
      "end": 593.06,
      "text": "너의 엄마와 너의 아빠가 우리를 좋아하지 않아서가 아닌 거야 라는 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.26,
      "end": 594.66,
      "text": "And then why did they leave us?"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.84,
      "end": 599.66,
      "text": "우리 엄마가, 아빠가 우리를 싫어해서 떠난 게 아니야 라는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.66,
      "end": 603.42,
      "text": "I just think they liked themselves better."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.6,
      "end": 606.24,
      "text": "나는 그저 이렇게 생각해."
    },
    {
      "start": 606.38,
      "end": 609.04,
      "text": "They liked themselves better."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.26,
      "end": 611.18,
      "text": "Oh, that's why they left."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.28,
      "end": 611.48,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.7,
      "end": 613.44,
      "text": "They didn't not like us."
    },
    {
      "start": 613.52,
      "end": 616.26,
      "text": "They just liked themselves more than us."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.38,
      "end": 616.76,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.76,
      "end": 617.52,
      "text": "They were selfish."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.52,
      "end": 622.42,
      "text": "Yeah, 이기적이긴 한데 그 내면을 다 이해할 수 있다라는 것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.42,
      "end": 622.98,
      "text": "민아가"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.98,
      "end": 624.14,
      "text": "She's grown up so well."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.22,
      "end": 625.32,
